data.text:
With a stay at Neutral Bay Lodge in Sydney (Neutral Bay), you'll be within a 15-minute walk of May Gibbs’ Nutcote and Ensemble Theatre. This hotel is 1 mi (1.6 km) from Cremorne Point to Mosman Bay Walk and 1.2 mi (2 km) from Olympic Pool North Sydney. Take in the views from a garden and make use of amenities such as complimentary wireless internet access and tour/ticket assistance. Featured amenities include a computer station, express check-in, and express check-out. Limited parking is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 19 guestrooms featuring minibars and LCD televisions. Prepare your meals in the shared/communal kitchen. Complimentary wired and wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming provides entertainment. Bathrooms have showers and complimentary toiletries.

Voir plus

With a stay at Rydges North Sydney in Sydney (North Sydney), you'll be a 3-minute drive from Sydney Harbour Bridge and 5 minutes from Circular Quay. This upscale hotel is 2.9 mi (4.7 km) from Hyde Park and 3 mi (4.9 km) from Overseas Passenger Terminal. This hotel offers designated smoking areas. At Rydges North Sydney, enjoy a satisfying meal at the restaurant. Quench your thirst with your favorite drink at the bar/lounge. Buffet breakfasts are served on weekdays from 7:00 AM to 9:30 AM and on weekends from 7:00 AM to 10:30 AM for a fee. Featured amenities include express check-out, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 168 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and minibars. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and cable programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with shower/tub combinations feature complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include phones, as well as safes and desks.

Voir plus

With a stay at Quest North Sydney in Sydney (North Sydney), you'll be within a 5-minute drive of Sydney Harbour Bridge and Luna Park. This upscale aparthotel is 1.5 mi (2.4 km) from Royal North Shore Hospital and 2.8 mi (4.4 km) from Circular Quay. Don't miss out on recreational opportunities including a sauna and a 24-hour fitness center. This aparthotel also features complimentary wireless internet access, concierge services, and a vending machine. Satisfy your appetite at Café Lost & Found, a restaurant where you can take in the garden view. Snacks are also available at the coffee shop/cafe. Featured amenities include a business center, complimentary newspapers in the lobby, and dry cleaning/laundry services. Planning an event in Sydney? This aparthotel has 732 square feet (68 square meters) of space consisting of conference space and 2 meeting rooms. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 100 air-conditioned rooms featuring kitchens with refrigerators and stovetops. Your room comes with a pillowtop bed. 55-inch Smart televisions with digital programming provide entertainment, while complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected. Conveniences include desks and separate sitting areas, as well as phones with free local calls.

Voir plus

Located in the heart of the city Central Business District. Citadines Walker North Sydney is at the epicentre of North Sydney commercial/retail/ social scenes/surrounded by bars/restaurants and healthcare services. Citadines Walker North Sydney will cater to business and leisure travellers in the commercial belt which will have over 130000 square metres of net lettable office space being added to the existing supply in the near term. It is in proximity to key public transportation including a train station and bus station. Citadines Walker North Sydney offers 252 rooms and facilities including a restaurant/meeting rooms/business centre/executive lounge and gymnasium. This residence or hotel has implemented the Ascott Cares 7 commitments to wellness cleanliness and sustainability. Visit www.discoverasr.com/en/wellness to find out more.

With a stay at North Sydney Hotel in Sydney (North Sydney), you'll be within a 5-minute drive of Sydney Harbour Bridge and Luna Park. This hotel is 3.1 mi (5 km) from Circular Quay and 3.2 mi (5.2 km) from Taronga Zoo. Take in the views from a terrace and make use of amenities such as complimentary wireless internet access. Enjoy a satisfying meal at Percy's serving guests of North Sydney Hotel. Wrap up your day with a drink at the bar/lounge. A complimentary continental breakfast is included. Featured amenities include luggage storage and ATM/banking services. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 13 air-conditioned rooms featuring Smart televisions. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and digital programming is available for your entertainment. Bathrooms have complimentary toiletries and hair dryers. Conveniences include irons/ironing boards, and housekeeping is provided daily.

This 5-star aparthotel is 1.2 mi (1.9 km) from Olympic Pool North Sydney and 1.2 mi (1.9 km) from Milsons Point Wharf. Don't miss out on the many recreational opportunities, including an indoor pool, a spa tub, and a sauna. This aparthotel also features complimentary wireless Internet access, concierge services, and a vending machine. Featured amenities include complimentary newspapers in the lobby, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Self parking (subject to charges) is available onsite. Make yourself at home in one of the 218 air-conditioned rooms featuring kitchens with full-sized refrigerators/freezers and ovens. Wired and wireless Internet access is complimentary, while 55-inch flat-screen televisions with digital programming provide entertainment. Conveniences include phones, as well as laptop-compatible safes and desks.
